column5: If anyone likes their show, I just saw what looks like all their shows uploaded to YouTube. A lot of the videos were uploaded really recently  https://www.youtube.com/user/Fishncanada/videos
Thanks, never saw it before, the episode I watched was good, have to look at more later.
I just started watching the series on YT, I never get a chance to catch it on TV.  I hope all fishing shows start uploading their series online.
